      "form_guide": "",
      "comment": "JACWILL KID (4) has joined Jason Grimson since winning both his heat and the Group 1 final of the Gold Crown series at Bathurst in March. Has impressively won two trials since then, the latest by a big space at this circuit and distance. He looks tough to stop off that. Unbeaten filly BIRDSONG (2) hasn't raced since recording her fourth straight win by taking out the G1 Gold Tiara final in March but has been readied with two strong trial wins at Menangle. Has the speed to take advantage of the low draw so must be a danger. AARDIES A STAR NZ (3) is a progressive former Kiwi who has won both times he has raced over this distance here. Draws to be involved again. Last-start Breeders Classic placegetter BETTOR ONE (1) tackles some smart ones here but is yet to miss the top-two and gets the ace draw.",
